e Poison Dood.<br><br>5.) Now this may seem silly, but, dammit, they get on my nerves... Has anyone ever thought about getting everyone in the Overthere Zone to gang up on, and beat the crap out of the Goons??? I know, I am game!!! Bloody bastitches!!!<br><br>6.) Next question... erm... I forgot... UGH... I will return again with more, I am sure.<br><br>Thank you all in advance, and as always, Good Hunting!!</p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />51 Druid<br>22 Necromancer<br>22 Beastlord<br>13 Rogue<br>Guild Leader of Darkwynde Legion located on Maelin Starpyre</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >6 Replies</td></tr></table>
