cult really.<br><br>6) The correct answer is Green.</p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br /><span class="sm">~WoW~<br><a href="HTTP://wow.allakhazam.com/profile.html?81141" target="akztarg">Cafeen</a> - Troll Hunter<br>&lt;<a href="HTTP://thefoot.guildwizard.com" target="akztarg">The Foot Clan</a>&gt;<br>Deathwing (PvP)<br><br>~EQ~<br><b><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=892149" target="akztarg">Stubbed Toez</a></b> - Overlord of Brell<br><b><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=283557" target="akztarg">Cafeen</a></b>- Tier'Dal Coercer<br>Member of &lt;<a href="HTTP://www.deluclin.com" target="akztarg">Descending Essence</a>&gt;<br>Luclin Server</span class="sm"></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8">Posting from the couch</td></tr></table>
